      "created_at": "2021-07-26T11:49:26.927Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Peja eshte Olimpi I shqiptareve <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/grinning.png?v=12\" title=\":grinning:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":grinning:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"><br>\nO moj Peja e Dardanise<br>\nJe Olimpi I shqiptarise<br>\nPoplli😀</p>",
