      "created_at": "2021-09-02T16:21:21.084Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Gol Kosova!!Challandes prape nuk i ndrit nuri <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/grinning.png?v=12\" title=\":grinning:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":grinning:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>",
