      "created_at": "2021-09-05T04:43:04.467Z",
      "cooked": "<p>sa e madhe te eshte vrima e bithes ty ,nashi vetem elefantet te bejne derman .</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": 35,
      "like_count": 0
