      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/a/2bfe46/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2021-09-05T04:50:56.256Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Te paska marre malli per elefantet, duket se ke qene vertet shume e zene me afganët. Po brothersat mos ler pas dore, t’u bëfsha, se i vënë zjarrin Amerikës.</p>",
