      "created_at": "2021-09-08T19:07:05.929Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Shume e terhequr Kosova.Hasmi duhet pritur ne mes te fushes,sa me larg portes <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/grinning.png?v=12\" title=\":grinning:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":grinning:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>",
