      "created_at": "2021-09-08T19:24:33.454Z",
      "cooked": "<p>ruhuni nga bolet e Marlonit qe jane të pranishme edhe ne futbollin modern ngambrapa:</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/2/d/2d1d28afe6cc1ba67edc5e1fc1b65f524e99a0f8.jpeg\" alt=\"caricature_warsaw_4\" data-base62-sha1=\"6r5Xs0j84VLSnQCFFEEdODv6Qu4\" width=\"562\" height=\"409\"></p>",
