      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/a/85e7bf/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2021-09-08T20:45:45.713Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Gjithe ato vite pa humbje e kur i duhet shqiptarise ata ose humbin ose barazojne.inglizi I mootit <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/joy.png?v=12\" title=\":joy:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":joy:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>",
